726831f-a.title: Queens: Greenpoint Avenue - Review Street
726831f-a.text:
Greenpoint Avenue, east from Review Avenue. View 2 shows the avenuek intersection with Van Dam Street (left). In the background is St. Raphaels Roaan Catholic Church, at Hunters Point
Avenue.
July 25, 1939
P.L. Sperr

726827f-a.title: Queens: Greenpoint Avenue - Van Dam Street
726827f-a.text:
Intersection of Greenpoint Avenue (right) and Van Dam Street (left), looking east from Review Avenue. Back on Greenpoint Avenue can be seen St. Raphaels (R.C.) Chureh.
P. L. Sperr  July 27, 1940
